      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473411\">H 14732</a> - And from him, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Mahboub, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, who has said:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> has said; ‘The government of the falsehood does not decline for a long time, and the government of the truth lasts for a short while’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "284. And from him, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Mahboub, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, who has said: Abu Abdullah (a.s.) has said; ‘The government of the falsehood does not decline for a long time, and the government of the truth lasts for a short while’."
        ]
